  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/ea27d8e791ad619ce5390d005dcf5e8c.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trouble in Warsaw is a short, detective game, combining the genres of Visual Novel and Point&Click, featuring many puzzles, dialogues and related choices solidifying the plot and its finale.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.poster.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.webm?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.mp4?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story takes place in contemporary Warsaw and tells the tale of a private detective, Karol Bielanski, who investigates the mysterious death of a wealthy real estate agent. The player, playing the role of the Detective, has to make hard and sometimes morally questionable choices to get to the truth behind the murder.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.poster.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.webm?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.mp4?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Engaging, non-linear storyline</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Inventory, allowing you to pick up, use and examine items you find</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environmental puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A world presenting real-life locations from Warsaw</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/ea27d8e791ad619ce5390d005dcf5e8c.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trouble in Warsaw is a short, detective game, combining the genres of Visual Novel and Point&Click, featuring many puzzles, dialogues and related choices solidifying the plot and its finale.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.poster.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.webm?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/47da820cfe077d4ddfcb000ed2a0f3ab.mp4?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story takes place in contemporary Warsaw and tells the tale of a private detective, Karol Bielanski, who investigates the mysterious death of a wealthy real estate agent. The player, playing the role of the Detective, has to make hard and sometimes morally questionable choices to get to the truth behind the murder.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.poster.avif?t=1738939043\" width=586 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.webm?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348240/extras/c621baf4de4a652f5aa7042353257216.mp4?t=1738939043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Engaging, non-linear storyline</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Inventory, allowing you to pick up, use and examine items you find</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environmental puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A world presenting real-life locations from Warsaw</p>",
